	<version>1.0.0</version>
	<description><![CDATA[
		<h1>Hello World (v.1.0.0)</h1>
		<div style="clear: both;"></div>
		<p>This component was built using Black Rabbit Component Creator for Free. <strong>Built for Joomla 3.0.</strong></p>
